methods.name: initApplication

args.name: stakedAssetId
args.desc: - The asset ID of the token to be staked in the pool.

args.name: rewardAssetId
args.desc: - The asset ID of the token to be distributed as rewards.

args.name: initialBalanceTxn
args.desc: - The payment transaction providing the initial minimum balance for the contract.

methods.desc:
Initializes the staking pool application with the specified staked asset and reward asset.

Sets up global state variables, verifies the initial funding payment, and opts the contract into the staked asset
and reward asset if necesary.
Only the admin address can call this function.
